title: Toilers of the Sea
creator: Victor Hugo
description: LibriVox recording of Toilers of the Sea, by Victor Hugo. This is the story of a man’s monumental struggle against nature, to win the hand of the woman he loves, and surmount every difficulty that Nature puts in his path (Summary by Alisson Veldhuis) M4B audiobook of complete book For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: LibriVox; Audiobooks; Adventure;Sea Story; Guersnsey
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
